                            <comment id="12486380" author="oysteing" created="Tue, 3 Apr 2007 16:02:48 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Attached patch, derby-2519.diff, contains the fixes described above.  All changes are in a single file:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;NOTE: It turned out that in order for the test to use ResultSet.updateClob, Clob.setString is needed.  This is not yet implemented in the embedded driver, but there is a patch for this (&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-2346&quot; title=&quot;Provide set methods for clob for embedded driver&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;DERBY-2346&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;DERBY-2346&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;) which is under review.  I will mark this issue as blocked by that &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-2346&quot; title=&quot;Provide set methods for clob for embedded driver&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;DERBY-2346&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;DERBY-2346&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, and not set the patch available flag until &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-2346&quot; title=&quot;Provide set methods for clob for embedded driver&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;DERBY-2346&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;DERBY-2346&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; has been committed.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12486382" author="oysteing" created="Tue, 3 Apr 2007 16:04:07 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Test change requires Clob.setString to run in embedded.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12491281" author="oysteing" created="Tue, 24 Apr 2007 14:24:33 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Clob.setString has now been implemented (by &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-2346&quot; title=&quot;Provide set methods for clob for embedded driver&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;DERBY-2346&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;DERBY-2346&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;), so this patch can now be considered for review/commit.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
